  MdeModulePkg/Universal/DevicePathDxe/DevicePathDxe.inf
  MdeModulePkg/Universal/DisplayEngineDxe/DisplayEngineDxe.inf
  MdeModulePkg/Universal/SetupBrowserDxe/SetupBrowserDxe.inf
